Add ability to provide token_fd for BPF_MAP_CREATE command through
bpf_map_create() API.

Also wire through token_create.allowed_map_types param for
BPF_TOKEN_CREATE command.

Signed-off-by: Andrii Nakryiko <andrii@kernel.org>
